marketing: Shell Naturelle S5 Grease V120P 2 is a fully synthetic biodegradeable grease for use in applications where environmental acceptability is required. This grease is based upon a lithium hydroxystearate soap thickener and is fortified with extreme pressure, anti-oxidant, anti-wear and anti-rust additives.
